race.description: Nzb Ready To Run 12 & 13 Nov Midway Hcp (C1)
race.comment: KOIOS (1) looks primed to fire fresh after two sharp trial wins leading in. Forget his final two runs last prep when clearly at the end, his earlier form was rock-solid and he now finds a very winnable race first-up. Maps for the gun run and can make an immediate impact. AUTUMN BLONDE (2) drops sharply in class after contesting the G2 Tea Rose and looks far better placed here. Boasts the race fitness edge and is an obvious threat. VALIANT BOMB (3) resumes off two nice trials and showed good ability in his debut prep. Draws kindly and can be right in the finish. AMARETTO BO (4) wasn't as effective last time but returns to where he bolted in first-up. Capable of bouncing straight back. TONG HO (5) can fill a minor placing if he brings his A-game.
